channel.title: Project V2
channel.description:
[b]Hello me and my team are working on a V2 of [url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,342814.0.html]Project[/url]. We currently released [url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,342814.0.html]Project[/url] last week.[/b] [hr] [i]Working on: PvP System - 50% done[IMG]http://i293.photobucket.com/albums/mm45/HappyScape/Project%20Happy/newtag.jpg[/img] Woodcutting Minigame [/i] [hr] [i]Completed: Fletching 100%[IMG]http://i293.photobucket.com/albums/mm45/HappyScape/Project%20Happy/newtag.jpg[/img] Mining 100%[IMG]http://i293.photobucket.com/albums/mm45/HappyScape/Project%20Happy/newtag.jpg[/img] Smithing 100%[IMG]http://i293.photobucket.com/albums/mm45/HappyScape/Project%20Happy/newtag.jpg[/img] Fishing 100%[IMG]http://i293.photobucket.com/albums/mm45/HappyScape/Project%20Happy/newtag.jpg[/img] Ranging 100%[IMG]http://i293.photobucket.com/albums/mm45/HappyScape/Project%20Happy/newtag.jpg[/img] Herblore 100%[IMG]http://i293.photobucket.com/albums/mm45/HappyScape/Project%20Happy/newtag.jpg[/img] Thieving 100%[IMG]http://i293.photobucket.com/albums/mm45/HappyScape/Project%20Happy/newtag.jpg[/img] Magic 100%[IMG]http://i293.photobucket.com/albums/mm45/HappyScape/Project%20Happy/newtag.jpg[/img] Cleaned source 1 Connection per IP 1 Basic shop Wilderness only in the actual wilderness 80% Working magic - Fixing the animations and adding it so you face the opponent on using the spell 100% Working magic teleports[IMG]http://i293.photobucket.com/albums/mm45/HappyScape/Project%20Happy/newtag.jpg[/img] Added a option so if you get stuck you can kill your self in the Quest Tab[IMG]http://i293.photobucket.com/albums/mm45/HappyScape/Project%20Happy/newtag.jpg[/img] Added 2 new options in Quest Tab to change to Ancients/Normal. -Uses 50% of Special Energy[IMG]http://i293.photobucket.com/albums/mm45/HappyScape/Project%20Happy/newtag.jpg[/img] Much more stable thieving from stalls[/i] [hr] [b]Server size un-compressed: 1.72MB[IMG]http://i293.photobucket.com/albums/mm45/HappyScape/Project%20Happy/newtag.jpg[/img] [b]Server size compressed: 267KB[IMG]http://i293.photobucket.com/albums/mm45/HappyScape/Project%20Happy/newtag.jpg[/img] [hr][center] [IMG]http://img7.imageshack.us/img7/5559/basicshopqe8.png[/img] [IMG]http://img222.imageshack.us/img222/904/2hitvz4.png[/img] [IMG]http://img7.imageshack.us/img7/3589/noglitchtq8.png[/img] [IMG]http://img222.imageshack.us/img222/7601/ancientsrx7.png[/img] [IMG]http://img7.imageshack.us/img7/4804/56355651vh1.png[/img] [/center]
[i]My team working on this project: K0killer2 PKN00B MMadny JekilD Fr33 $ LOL $ SWAT Slypher [V]agrent ']['he.Sex[/i]
If you have [b]any[/b] suggestions please post!
